inlineContent.text: Apple provides the BLAS and LAPACK libraries under the Accelerate framework to be in line with LAPACK 3.9.1. Starting with iOS 19, iPadOS 19, macOS 16, tvOS 19, watchOS 19, and visionOS 3, the libraries are in line with LAPACK 3.12.0. These new interfaces provide additional functionality, as well as a new ILP64 interface. To use the new interfaces, define

as preprocessor macros in Xcode build settings.
